        Doorways is a survival horror game in which nothing is what it
        seems. With diverse enigmas, changing gameplay and the scariest

        Everything is diffuse. What's real? What kind of nightmare is

        Will you unveil the different misteries while your deepest fears
        lurk upon you? Will you step through the gates without knowing
        where they lead to? In Doorways, every threshold will get you to
        a different world.

        fears that you would expect from these types of games, while
        testing your tolerance to horror and your capacity to solve
        problems under pressure. Do you think you have what it takes to
        survive?
